---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-white/10 bg-dark py-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-bold font-mono tracking-tighter text-white inline-block mb-4">
          MD<span class="text-accent">MRON</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-sm mb-6 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Curating dark techno experiences and industrial soundscapes. Event organizer and DJ based in the underground scene.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/manana.ala/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:border-accent transition-all">
